Implemented scoped fixes and wrote `.review-slices/H09.fix.md`. I did not run build/test commands because the slice explicitly forbids them.
  ✓ Verify findings against cited code
  ✓ Patch narrow source fixes under packages/actions
  ✓ Review diffs without git and write fix report
diff --git a/.review-slices/H09.fix.md b/.review-slices/H09.fix.md
